summary: BIGGEST CHAD PRIVILEGE - A few days from launch, the biggest holder will have the chance to do something truly unique—alter the token's name to proudly showcase their bag, send a message to the entire crypto community, or maybe even provoke a reaction from someone and invite him to the measuring contest. With a lot of inches comes great power, and the biggest Chad will be respected as it should be. As we progress into later phases, the top inches holder will unlock even more exclusive perks and prizes.
